body:
Avicus as we know is shutting down, as sad as this may be i will hope to stick around with some of the players.

This is a AMA so yeh ama but i also want to thank a few people for making my time on avicus the best it could be, if i were ti say reasons for all these people it would take ages so hears a list.
Power_pixel
Rakkio
Mels
Sweedie
Xtra
Komodolord1
Atditc
2bj
MemySelfAndGhost
Avia
Hivu
SpacePandaOG
Lokigh
Wolfie
Kr0vax
SpyTed (zWifieeeee)
Jarvo 
And last but not least Michah!! 

Thanks for all the memes and dreams you've brought me if ive mist you out pls no hate pms xD, 

Goodbye Avicus 2018 25th jan!

AMA -coco
